snippet.title: Dino Storm | Trailer 2021
snippet.description:
Fame and fortune awaits brave adventurers in the free 3D MMOG Dino Storm. With just a few dollars in your pocket, a little ammunition, a loaded laser cannon, and your small dinosaur, you make your way to DinoVille. Face gigantic herds of dinosaurs and merciless bandits. Start your thrilling search for valuable items. Set up supply camps, outposts, and goldmines, defend them against other players, and earn fame and respect. Only the best will manage to become the sheriff of the town.

Play now for free in your browser at http://www.dinostorm.com  

--------------------

A big thanks goes to Dartank/Eredin who created this new trailer showing a more up to date "Dino Storm" with many new elements & areas added to the game. Link to his channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC8ZzCNdOX1JPG1reKuQV9ZQ
